data.description: Spacious 2 Bedroom 2 full Bath Island Home. Are you looking for a unique and cozy island home with plenty of space and amenities?  Look no further than this custom-built-house in a premiere HOA community.  This house has everything you need to enjoy the island lifestyle, from fireplace made with local shale to a covered barbecue area for outdoor fun.  You'll love the imported porcelain tile, the granite countertops, the rough sawn ceder ceilings, and vinyl plank floors that give this house a rustic charm.  The master bedroom has a separate sewing room, an exercise room with a porch, and a loft accessed by a ladder. The main office has sliding glass doors that offer a stunning view of the barbecue area. The two-car garage has an electric door opener and plenty of storage space. There is another air conditioned office with access from the garage or an outside doorway. The HOA fees are only $600 a year and include your sewer service and use of the exclusive community boat ramp and dock. The drinking water is pure and comes from the island's reverse osmois plant. This house is a one-of-a-kind gem that you don't want to miss.  Schedule a showing today.
